<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.10">
<l>tiṇkaḷaka matiḷpuṭaicūḻ tirunaṟaiyūr niṉṟāṉai</l>
<l>vaṇkaḷaka nilaveṟikkum vayalmaṅkai nakarāḷaṉ</l>
<l>paṇkaḷakam payiṉṟacīrppā ṭalivaipat tumvallār</l>
<l>viṇkaḷakat timaiyavarāy vīṟṟiruntu vāḻvārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten fine songs which practice the melodies of love</l>
<l>By the ruler of the city of Maṅkai, with fields where beautiful swans</l>
<l rend="indent">reflect the moonlight,</l>
<l>About the one who stands in Tirunaṟaiyūr, its sides encircled</l>
<l rend="indent">by strong, mortared walls,</l>
<l>Being enthroned as never-blinking [celestials], they will dwell in the heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
